# WorkoutTracker iOS App - Project Structure

## Main Entry Points
- [WorkoutTrackerApp.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/WorkoutTrackerApp.swift) - Main app entry point with SwiftData configuration and URL handling
- [ContentView.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/ContentView.swift) - Root view that manages tab navigation and state
- [AppDelegate.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/AppDelegate.swift) - Handles push notifications and app lifecycle

## Core Data Model
- [Workout.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/Workout.swift) - SwiftData model for workout entities

## Main Views by Tab
- [CompletedView.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/CompletedView.swift) - Shows completed workouts
- [LapsedView.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/LapsedView.swift) - Shows missed/lapsed workouts  
- [UpcomingView.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/UpcomingView.swift) - Shows future scheduled workouts
- [CalendarTabView.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/CalendarTabView.swift) - Calendar interface
- [SettingsView.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/SettingsView.swift) - App settings and configuration

## Workout Management
- [AddWorkout.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/AddWorkout.swift) - Complex form for adding new workouts with location picker
- [EditWorkoutView.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/EditWorkoutView.swift) - Edit existing workouts
- [WorkoutView.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/WorkoutView.swift) - Individual workout display
- [WorkoutsView.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/WorkoutsView.swift) - List view for workouts
- [WorkoutsViewHStack.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/WorkoutsViewHStack.swift) - Horizontal workout cards

## Settings & Configuration
- [WorkoutTypeSetting.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/WorkoutTypeSetting.swift) - Manage workout categories
- [WorkoutTemplateSetting.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/WorkoutTemplateSetting.swift) - Manage workout templates
- [AppearanceSetting.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/AppearanceSetting.swift) - Dark/light mode settings
- [FavouritesSetting.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/FavouritesSetting.swift) - Favourite workout management

## Navigation & UI Components
- [BottomBarView.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/BottomBarView.swift) - Tab bar navigation
- [ToolbarView.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/ToolbarView.swift) - Common toolbar components
- [CalendarView.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/CalendarView.swift) - Calendar implementation
- [DayDetailView.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/DayDetailView.swift) - Daily workout details

## External Integrations
- [LinkToStrava.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/LinkToStrava.swift) - Strava OAuth integration
- [SyncToiCloud.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/SyncToiCloud.swift) - iCloud sync functionality
- [PushNotifications.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/PushNotifications.swift) - Notification handling

## Utilities & Helpers
- [KeychainHelper.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/KeychainHelper.swift) - Secure token storage
- [KeyboardResponder.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/KeyboardResponder.swift) - Keyboard management
- [SwipeActionsAndAlertsModifiers.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/SwipeActionsAndAlertsModifiers.swift) - Common UI modifiers
- [SwipeDownToDismissModifier.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/SwipeDownToDismissModifier.swift) - Gesture handling

## Key Features
- SwiftData for persistence with optional iCloud sync
- Location services with MapKit integration
- Strava OAuth integration
- Push notifications
- Dark/light mode support
- Workout templates
- Favourites system
- Calendar view
- Search and filtering
